data.description: Solera @ Kern Canyon - gated 55+ community with resort-style living at its best. Want your own pool for the hot summer days?  This is the perfect home with a beautiful pool with waterfall. Freshly painted interior and ready for new owner. Features 2 bedrooms plus office/den and 2 baths.  Great room with fireplace & sliding doors to covered patio opens to dining area and kitchen. Kitchen with granite counters, bar, newer stainless steel refrigerator, microwave, dishwasher & pantry.  Indoor laundry with sink and cabinets. Shutters & fans throughout. You'll enjoy the low maintenance backyard with pool. Oversized 2 car garage.  Community clubhouse, gym, pool, spa, tennis, pickle ball and bocce courts plus many interest clubs and activities to participate.
